                <div type="textpart" subtype="work" n="1">
                    <pb n="16"/>

                    <ab><title xml:lang="la" ana="#incerta">ANNALES SAMIORUM.</title></ab>

                    <p n="1">In Samo feras fuisse tradunt, tant&#230; vocis, ut clamando rumperent
                        terram. Appellabantur Neides, ut Eugeon narrat.</p>

                    <p n="2">Eugeon patrem Homeri dicit Meletem.</p>

                    <p n="3">&#198;sopum Eugeon Mesembrianum dicit.</p>
